es erreurs\u00bb, reconna\u00eet Daniel Green|last1=Ouellette V\u00e9zina|first1=Henri|date=4 November 2019|work=[[M\u00e9tro (Montreal newspaper)|M\u00e9tro]]|accessdate=9 January 2020|language=French|quote=Est-il int\u00e9ress\u00e9 par un \u00e9ventuel poste de chef du Parti vert? \u00abPas du tout, tranche le principal int\u00e9ress\u00e9. J\u2019ai 64 ans et \u00eatre un chef de parti, c\u2019est un sport extr\u00eame. Je vais laisser \u00e0 d\u2019autres, peut-\u00eatre plus jeunes, mener le parti vers d\u2019autres horizons, plus grands et plus forts.\u00bb Translation : Is he interested in becoming leader of the Green Party? \"Not at all,\" ruled the person in question. I'm 64 years old and being a party leader is an extreme sport. I'm going to let others, maybe younger, lead the party to new bigger and stronger horizons.}}</ref>\n*[[Paul Manly]], MP for [[Nanaimo\u2014Ladysmith]] (2019\u2013present)<ref>{{cite news |last1=Pablo |first1=Carlito |title=B.C. MP Paul Manly takes a pass at leadership of Green Party of Canada |url=https://www.straight.com/news/1324551/bc-mp-paul-manly-takes-pass-leadership-green-party-canada |accessdate=21 November 2019 |publisher=[[The Georgia Straight]] |date=13 November 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Pierre Nantel]], Green Party candidate for [[Longueuil\u2014Saint-Hubert]] in 2019, former [[New Democratic Party|New Democratic]] MP for [[Longueuil\u2014Saint-Hubert]] (2015\u20132019), [[Longueuil\u2014Saint-Hubert|Longueuil\u2014Pierre-Boucher]] (2011\u20132015)<ref name=\"Nantel\">{{cite web|url=http://www.tvrs.ca/blog/pierre-nantel-reflechit-a-se-presenter-comme-chef-du-parti-vert|title=Pierre Nantel r\u00e9fl\u00e9chit \u00e0 se pr\u00e9senter comme chef du Parti vert|last=|first=|date=November 5, 2019|website=TVRS|language=fr|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=November 7, 2019|quote=Pierre Nantel is considering running for Green Party leader}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lecourrierdusud.ca/pierre-nantel-ne-s